<ROUTINE DRILLED-HOLE-F ("AUX" OBJ)
	 <SET OBJ <COND (<EQUAL? ,HERE ,COMMANDERS-QUARTERS>
			 ,SAFE)
			(<EQUAL? ,HERE ,LOAN-SHARK>
			 ,STRONG-BOX)
			(T
			 ,HOUSING)>>
